1
00:00:00,600 --> 00:00:02,000
I had to burn it.

2
00:00:02,501 --> 00:00:04,000
All of it.

3
00:00:04,001 --> 00:00:06,000
Murkoff took so much from us.

4
00:00:06,801 --> 00:00:08,000
Used us.

5
00:00:09,301 --> 00:00:15,200
Turned us into these things because nobody
cares about a few forgotten lunatics.

6
00:00:15,701 --> 00:00:17,000
So let it burn.

7
00:00:17,801 --> 00:00:21,000
Burn the whole goddamn thing down.

8
00:00:21,801 --> 00:00:23,000
Get out.

9
00:00:23,001 --> 00:00:27,000
If you want to let you get
out through the kitchen.

